 For NYSP sites, certification from the sponsor that all of the
children who will receive Program meals are enrolled participants in
the NYSP;

 The extent of Program payments needed, including a request for
advance payments and start-up payments, if applicable, and a
staffing and monitoring plan;

 A statement that the eligibility standards conform to the
Secretary's family size and income standards for reduced price
